#   - Public Key:  assets/functions/xeroAPI/certs/publickey_ecig.cer
#
# NO environment variables needed for Xero - it uses certificate auth
# Consumer Key: 3IF7NH5MGURJIPI1PRRVOMX2KVZJHX (hardcoded in credentials file)

# ============================================================================
